quran[31]{c,v,t}:
  49,14,"Ma-Arab a lehoatateng a re: “Re’a kholoa.” E re: “Ha le na tumelo; le mpa le re “Re inehetse Islamong,” hobane tumelo ha es’o finyelle lipelong tsa lona. Hobane haeba le mamela Allah le Moromuoa oa Hae, Allah A ke ke A le qhekella meputsong ea liketso tsa lona. Hobane Allah U Ts’oarela joalo-joalo, U Tletse Mohau"
  49,15,"Ba-kholoang ka ‘nete ke ba kholoang feela ho Allah le ho Moromuoa oa Hae, ba se na khoao, empa ba tsitlalletse ka tseo ba nang le tsona le ka maphelo a bona ts’ebeletsong ea Allah. Ba joalo ke ba nang ‘nete"
  49,16,"E re: “Na le ka ruta Allah tumelo ea lona? Empa Allah U na le tsebo tsohle tse maholimong le tsohle tse lefats’eng, U Hlokolosi ka lintho tsohle"
  49,17,"Ba u tiisetsa hore ba inehetse Islamong e le ho u khahlisa, E re “Le se nahane hore tumelo ea lona e molemo ho ‘na, Che, Allah U le sitsitse ka lereko hore e be U le tataiselitse Tumelong, haeba le na le ‘nete ebile le hloekile lipelong"
  49,18,Ruri! Allah U tseba liphiri tsa maholimo le lefats’e. Etsoe Allah U bona tsohle tseo le li etsang.”
  50,1,"Qaf: Ka Qura‘n e tlotlehang (u morumuoa oa Allah)"
  50,2,"Empa ba maketse hore na ho tlile morumuoa ho bona ea hlahang har’a bona. Kahoo mahana-tumelo ba re: “ena ke ntho e makatsang"
  50,3,"Eng! Mohlang re shoang, re fetohile lerole, re ka boela ra tsosoa hape? Seo ke poelo e thoko haholo.”"
  50,4,"Re tseba tseo lefats’e le li jereng tsa bona, Re na le Lenane la litlaleho"
  50,5,Empa ba nyelisa ‘nete nakong eo e tlang ho bona; kahoo ba pherekanong
  50,6,Na ha ba shebeng marung holim’a bona? – Kamoo Re a entseng kateng le kamoo Re’a khabisitseng kateng; le kamoo ho senang sekoli kateng
  50,7,"Le lefats’e Re le alile le hona ho tsepamisa lithaba holim’a lona, eaba Re etsa hore limela tsohle tse khahlehang li mele holim’a lona, –"
  50,8,"E le pontso le sona sehopotso molemong oa lekhabunyane lefe, kapa lefe le sokolohileng"
  50,9,Re romella pula e hlohonolofetseng lefats’eng eo ka eona re phelisang lijalo lirapeng le tsona lijo thollo
  50,10,Le lifate tsa lipalema tse jereng liririella tsa litholoana; –
  50,11,Ele phepo molemong oa batho; e bile Re phelisa lefats’e le omeletseng ka pula. Ka mokhoa oo Tsoho Ea Bafu e tla bang kateng
  50,12,"Batho ba habo Nooe ba ile ba nyefola ‘nete pele ho bona, ka mokhoa o ts’oanang le baahi ba Rass, Ba – Thamude"
  50,13,"Ba – a’ad, Faro, le bana ba bo Lota"
  50,14,"Le baahi ba Mediane, le batho ba Tubb’a: morabe o mong le o mong o ile oa nyefola baromuoa; Tlhokomeliso ea Ka e ile ea phethahatsoa(holim’a bona)"
  50,15,Na Re ile Ra tepella ke tlholeho ea mathomo? Hore ebe ba na le khoao ka tlholeho e ncha
  50,16,"Ke Rona ba hlotseng motho, Re tseba ka botlalo seo moea oa hae o mo hlohleletsang sona, etsoe Re haufi haholo le eena ho feta mahalapa a hae"
  50,17,"Hopola manyeloi a mabeli a khethiloe ho ngola liketso tsa motho, le leng le lutse ka letsohong le letona, ha le leng lona le lutse ka letsohong le lets’ehali"
  50,18,Ha ho lentsoe leha le le leng leo a le buoang e be moalosi oa hae ha a le ngole
  50,19,"Mahlomola a lefu a tlisa ‘nete(kapel’a mahlo a hae): “Sena ke sona seo u neng u leka ho se qoba.”"
  50,20,"Terompeta e tla letsoa: Lena ke letsatsi le ts’episitsoeng"
  50,21,Moea ka mong o tla atamela le lenyeloi le o qhobang esitana le la paki
  50,22,"(Ho tla thoe;) “Ha u e’a ka oa tsotella molaetsa ona. Hajoale Re phetlile sekhurumetso sa lona, mahlo a lona a ncho-cho kajeno.”"
  50,23,"Moalosi oa hae o tla re: “tlaleho ea hae ke na le eona.”"
  50,24,"(Kahlolo e tla ba:) “akhelang mong le mong eo e leng molatoli oa Allah kahar’a lihele! –"
  50,25,"Ea neng a sitisa toka, a tlola meeli eohle, a jala khoao le lipelaelo,”"
  50,26,“Le hona ho iketsetsa molingoana kantle ho Allah. Mo akheleng kahar’a kahlolo e ts’abehang.”